ZH: 这瓶药水能治感冒。
EN: This bottle of medicine can cure a cold.

ZH: 他一喝这种药水就感觉好多了。
EN: He felt much better after drinking this medicine.

ZH: 这种药水对肚子痛很有效。
EN: This medicine is very effective for stomachaches.

ZH: 医生建议我喝这种药水。
EN: The doctor recommended that I drink this medicine.

ZH: 这瓶药水的味道很难喝。
EN: The taste of this bottle of medicine is very unpleasant.

ZH: 这瓶药水需要放在阴凉处保存。
EN: This bottle of medicine needs to be stored in a cool place.

ZH: 请记住每次喝药水的时间。
EN: Remember the time you drink the medicine each time.

ZH: 请不要过量服用这种药水。
EN: Please do not overdose on this medicine.

ZH: 这种药水可以减轻头痛的症状。
EN: This medicine can relieve symptoms of headaches.

ZH: 我们需要去药店买一瓶药水。
EN: We need to go to the pharmacy to buy a bottle of medicine.

ZH: 请把这个药水给病人喝。
EN: Please give this medicine to the patient to drink.

ZH: 这种药水可以降低烧的温度。
EN: This medicine can reduce fever temperature.

ZH: 这种药水是中草药配制而成的。
EN: This medicine is prepared with traditional Chinese herbs.

ZH: 在饭前服用这种药水可以减少胃部不适。
EN: Taking this medicine before meals can reduce stomach discomfort.

ZH: 这种药水很容易引起过敏反应。
EN: This medicine can easily cause allergic reactions.

ZH: 这盒药水已经过期了，不能再服用。
EN: This box of medicine has expired and should not be used any longer.

ZH: 医生说服用这种药水后应该多喝水。
EN: The doctor said to drink more water after taking this medicine.

ZH: 这种药水是在药学实验室中研制出来的。
EN: This medicine was developed in a pharmaceutical laboratory.

ZH: 这种药水可以用来清洁伤口。
EN: This medicine can be used to clean wounds.

ZH: 我不喜欢这种味道苦涩的药水。
EN: I don't like the taste of this bitter medicine.
